WEBVTT

00:03:29.262 --> 00:03:33.034
to a neo-feudalist rentier society

00:03:33.034 --> 00:03:35.019
like 18th-century France.

00:03:35.019 --> 00:03:38.213
That was France

00:03:38.213 --> 00:03:39.960
before the revolution

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.984
and the mobs with the pitchforks.

00:03:41.984 --> 00:03:44.538
So I have a message for my fellow plutocrats

00:03:44.538 --> 00:03:46.360
and zillionaires

00:03:46.360 --> 00:03:47.834
and for anyone who lives

00:03:47.834 --> 00:03:50.070
in a gated bubble world:

00:03:50.070 --> 00:03:51.421
Wake up.

00:03:51.421 --> 00:03:55.141
Wake up. It cannot last.

00:03:55.141 --> 00:03:57.160
Because if we do not do something

00:03:57.160 --> 00:04:01.491
to fix the glaring economic inequities in our society,